OL,7,FThe Royal Mint has revealed a new 50p
OL,8,Fcoin depicting the Snowman - with a
OL,9,Fgold version hidden in one of its
OL,10,Fadvent calendars for someone to
OL,11,Fdiscover on Christmas Eve.
OL,13,FTo further celebrate the launch of The
OL,14,FSnowman 2024 collectable 50p, the Mint
OL,15,Fsaid it has hidden a solid gold coin
OL,16,Fbehind door 24 in one limited-edition
OL,17,FThe Snowman advent calendar, offering
OL,18,Fsomeone the chance of "striking gold".
