OL,7,FThe Snowman 50p coin is available in a
OL,8,Frange of precious metal finishes,
OL,9,Fincluding colour editions, on the
OL,10,FRoyal Mint's website, with prices
OL,11,Fstarting at #12. It will not be
OL,12,Fentering general circulation.
OL,14,FThe advent calendars will be priced at
OL,15,F#30, with a total of 3,000 available `
OL,16,Fand only one will have a gold proof
OL,17,Fcoin of The Snowman hidden inside.
