OL,7,FThe new coin celebrates Raymond
OL,8,FBriggs' picture book with a new design
OL,9,Fcreated by Robin Shaw, who was art
OL,10,Fdirector on The Snowman And The
OL,11,FSnowdog, the sequel to the original
OL,12,Ftelevision adaptation.
OL,14,FThis year's reverse (tails) design
OL,15,Fshows The Snowman decorating a
OL,16,FChristmas tree.
OL,18,FA selection of the coins will feature
OL,19,Fcolour, bringing the story to life on
OL,20,Fthe small canvas of a 50p coin.
