OL,7,FSince The Snowman first appeared on a
OL,8,FRoyal Mint 50p in 2018, close to
OL,9,F700,000 coins featuring the character
OL,10,Fhave made their way into collections
OL,11,Fglobally across 75 different
OL,12,Fcountries, the Mint said.
OL,14,FRebecca Morgan, director of
OL,15,Fcommemorative coin at the Royal Mint,
OL,16,Fsaid: "The Snowman collectable 50p has
OL,17,Fbecome a Christmas tradition at the
OL,18,FRoyal Mint, and we are delighted to
OL,19,Fcontinue this much-loved story on UK
OL,20,Fcoinage.
