OL,7,F"This year marks The Snowman's seventh
OL,8,Fappearance on a 50p, and Robin Shaw's
OL,9,Fspecial design expertly captures the
OL,10,Fmagic of Christmas."
OL,12,FMr Shaw said: "It's an honour to see
OL,13,Fone of my designs appear once again on
OL,14,Fa 50 pence piece.
OL,16,F"This year's Snowman coin captures the
OL,17,Fmagic of Raymond Briggs' most enduring
OL,18,Fcreation while celebrating The
OL,19,FSnowman's latest adventure on UK
OL,20,Fcoins."
