OL,7,FFirst published in 1978 as a wordless
OL,8,Fpicture book, The Snowman has since
OL,9,Fsold 5.5 million copies worldwide.
OL,11,FThe book inspired an animated short
OL,12,Ffilm that was first broadcast on
OL,13,FChannel 4 on December 26 1982.
