OL,7,FThomas Merrington, creative director,
OL,8,FPenguin Ventures, said: "Raymond
OL,9,FBriggs' The Snowman is a beloved and
OL,10,Fmagical story that captures the hearts
OL,11,Fof many families at Christmas every
OL,12,Fyear and we are thrilled our
OL,13,Fpartnership with the Royal Mint
OL,14,Fcontinues to flourish with the release
OL,15,Fof this seventh coin."
OL,17,FFrom November 11, Snowman fans will
OL,18,Falso be able to strike their own 50p
OL,19,Ffeaturing The Snowman at the Royal
OL,20,FMint Experience, based in Llantrisant
OL,21,Fin South Wales.
